		</div><!-- .comment-author .vcard -->
		
		<div class="comment-body"><p>Peer-review science supports global warming, and supports many topics influenced by politics, professors with an agenda, and other special interest groups. Trusting your life on peer-reviewed science is a risk.</p>
<p>Flu shots are BS and they protect nobody. The virus mutates and changes from person to person, science cannot predict the exact strain you will be exposed to during a flu season. It&#8217;s one wild ass guess which strain will hit you.</p>
</div>

